## 2. ✨ **FEATURE ENHANCEMENTS**

### **Feature 1: Energy Tracking**
```cpp
void trackEnergyConsumption() {
  static uint32_t lastUpdateTime = 0;
  uint32_t now = millis() / 1000;

  if (state.heizungAktiv && state.batterieLeistung > 0) {
    uint32_t deltaTime = now - lastUpdateTime;
    float deltaEnergy_Wh = (state.batterieLeistung * deltaTime) / 3600.0f;
    rtcData.gesamtEnergie_Wh += deltaEnergy_Wh;

    Serial.printf("Energy accumulated: %.2f Wh\n", rtcData.gesamtEnergie_Wh);
  }
  lastUpdateTime = now;
}
```

### **Feature 2: Low Battery Alert**
```cpp
#define BATTERY_LOW_VOLTAGE 10.5f
