| Interval-based sensor reading | Power savings (30-40%) | 🔴 High |
| RTC data validation with CRC | Data integrity | 🔴 High |
| SoftwareSerial on-demand init | Power savings (10-15%) | 🟡 Medium |
| INA226 calibration register | Current accuracy | 🟡 Medium |
