## 1. ⚙️ Modular Architecture

### Before (Monolithic)
```cpp
// Single 500+ line .ino file
void setup() {
  // 50 lines of initialization
}
void loop() {} // Never reached
```

### After (Modular)
```
├── config.h              // Configuration constants
├── types.h               // Data structures & enums
├── ina226_optimized.h    // Battery monitor
├── sensors.h             // Sensor manager
├── display_manager.h     // Display controller
├── wbus_controller.h     // W-BUS communication
├── power_manager.h       // Energy tracking
├── data_manager.h        // RTC data & CRC
└── main_optimized.ino    // Main sketch (< 200 lines)
